OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine, warm
OL,6,Fand mostly clear in the south, though
OL,7,Fcloud thickens across Wales and the
OL,8,Fsouthwest with some fog. Cloudy
OL,9,Ffurther north with rain, heaviest in
OL,10,Fwestern and northwestern Scotland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FRain persists across northern
OL,13,Fand northwestern Scotland. Cloudy at
OL,14,Ffirst across Northern Ireland and
OL,15,Fnorthern England with patchy drizzle.
OL,16,FElsewhere, sunny spells. Very warm and
OL,17,Flocally hot in the southeast.
